<br>
Any post that is posted after the date and time of the last edit of these posted rules will mean that you agree to abide by these policies.<br>
<br>
I hope everyone understand why these rules are being added. Let's continue having fun on the board and stop the unnecessary flames.<br>
<br>
Remember you are a guest here, act like one.<br>
<br>
1) If you start a flame thread in any other forum than Flames And Rants, the administrator or moderators will move it to the &quot;right&quot; forum or just delete it. Repeatedly breaking the rules will lead to your being banned.<br>
<br>
2) If you reply with a flame in any other forum than Flames And Rants, the administrator or moderators will delete it. Repeatedly breaking the rules will lead to your being banned.<br>
<br>
3)  Profanity in ANY form or variation is NOT allowed on any of the forums except for Flames And Rants, and even there should be minimal. Repeatedly breaking the rules will lead to your being banned. Hate words of a racial, religious, or sexual preference nature will be edited on sight, no matter where they appear.<br>
<br>
4) Anything deemed sexually or racially discriminating, or of an equally offensive nature will be deleted and the administrator and moderators may choose to ban the author. <br>
<br>
5) Adult material is NOT allowed. Pornographic stories, pictures, violent stories, etc. are NOT allowed. Post them and they will get deleted. Repeatedly breaking the rules will lead to your being banned.<br>
<br>
6) The administrator and moderators are allowed to delete and modify posts/threads and/or ban you without giving an explanation.<br>
<br>
7) The administrator and moderators may add/change/remove rules whenever they please. When new rules are added and the date of your new post is after the date, you are agreeing to the new posted/updated rules.<br>
<br>
